data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3-bedroom ranch home, offering a versatile basement room that can serve as a fourth bedroom or office, providing flexibility to suit your needs. Step inside to discover an open-concept layout, perfect for family fun and gatherings, with a spacious kitchen featuring a large island for convenient meal preparation and entertaining.  The master bedroom boasts a luxurious ensuite bathroom with a standing shower separate from the tub, along with a generous walk-in closet for added convenience. Say goodbye to basement trips for laundry, as the laundry area is conveniently located on the first floor.  Outside, the fenced backyard offers ample space for outdoor activities and customization, with the potential to build a patio, install a pool, or even add a half basketball court, making it a perfect oasis for relaxation and recreation.  Don't miss the opportunity to explore all the wonderful features this beautiful home has to offer. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself living in this delightful space! BATVAI
